Hammerson Gets Sheffield Agreement on City Center Plan, FT Says

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-06-03T01:05:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-03/hammerson-gets-sheffield-agreement-on-city-center-plan-ft-says.html
Hammerson Plc (HMSO)  has signed an agreement
with the Sheffield city council that allows the U.K. real estate
investment trust to begin construction of a 500 million-pound
city-center retail complex, the Financial Times reported, citing
a Hammerson spokesman.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 